name: DYOR Token
description: DYOR Project's motto is Educate, Equip, Empower. DYOR Project strives to teach investors how to find reputable crypto projects while avoiding scams. The DYOR Project team is currently developing a web utility that will include crypto charting, token contract scanners, and educational materials. Their goal is to teach the crypto community how to avoid the abundant fraud in the cryptocurrency space. The DYOR Project website and application are managed by DYOR Project based in the United States.
